      correct: 1,
      rationale: "Women with prior GDM have approximately 50% risk of developing T2DM within 10 years. This patient already has prediabetes (HbA1c 5.9%). Annual monitoring with HbA1c or FPG, intensive lifestyle counseling, and consideration of metformin are indicated."
